<ResourceDictionary xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

    <!--
        Fluence brand icons as resolution-independent vector DrawingImages. These replace the
        embedded multi-resolution Fluence.ico (which was ~42% of the library binary) and back both
        the default FluenceWindow.Icon (rasterized for the Win32 taskbar HICON) and the theme-aware
        Light/Dark window-icon examples. The geometries are reproduced verbatim from the authored
        source under assets\ with clean resource keys.
        
        - FluenceIconBrandDrawingImage : the colorful mark on its own, with no surrounding plate
        (the brand glyph). Used as the default window icon and the demo home hero.
        - FluenceIconLightDrawingImage : the mark on a light rounded plate, for use on dark chrome.
        - FluenceIconDarkDrawingImage  : the mark on a dark rounded plate, for use on light chrome.
    -->

